<p><b>The Recipes</b><br>
	The recipe tells the player which items he needs to catch to get a good score. The player can select which recipe he wants to play from the start screen. Each recipe has a different amount of slots and different required ingredients. Some of the required ingredients are optional, and the player can choose what sort of ingredient attributes he wants to collect. Once the player has caught enough ingredients to fill all the slots, the game is over and the score is revealed.</p>	
	
<p><b>Game Over</b><br>
	When the game ends, the player will get a score based on how well they did sticking to the recipe. The player also gets a score based on what the attributes were of the ingredients they caught as they were making the recipe.</p>	
	
